{"tid":1455701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者快啲問公安條例中既特務警察係乜黎","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:22:47.000Z","uid":56624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a175df65a83261387e6ec1612e7b8b1100817d24","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄧狗話用公務員事務局招聘警察，咁呢個咩嚟？？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n40.行政長官授權他人委任特務警察的權力<br />\n<br />\n行政長官可隨時藉命令授權警務處處長，以書面方式委任任何願意擔任特務警察的人為特務警察，任期由行政長官在該命令中指明。<br />\n<br />\n(由1970年第31號第25條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)"},{"pid":"a25a17ef04d571efa36de947cce038777eb4da12","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"89dc00ebb7a78078178c8d74a53d3927eae91d4e","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:04.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"f3dc4f85014ee44b0c27f7c4c20df7bd4f35dc7a","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:16.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"b03ddbc4d8f84f80e8101c59b2324dfc07503dc3","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"007106376d48ca5a97cfce606b0e25e953b2ebcf","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:41.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"729d3067954d6446c4e2aca8b9b79883ef5fb9b6","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"dab374b4eb1b9891086e6e3d002b865115da9995","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"591c42efbc0b304cf45e8b60c806a359c3f5fce1","tid":1455701,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:19:15.0